{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h1 id=\"data-input\"><a href=\"#data-input\" aria-label=\"data input permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Data input</h1>\n<p>Data input controls allow the user to provide information by selecting from a known set of options or a constrained format/value range.  </p>\n<p><strong>Selection controls:</strong> <a href=\"#checkbox\">Checkboxes</a>, <a href=\"#radio-buttons\">Radio buttons</a>, <a href=\"#select-lists\">Select lists</a>, <a href=\"#switch\">Switch</a></p>\n<p><strong>Bound-entry controls:</strong> Bound entry controls like <a href=\"#date-picker\">date picker</a> and <a href=\"#slider\">slider</a> are <em>in progress and coming soon</em> to PatternFly 4.</p>\n<h2 id=\"usage-selection-controls\"><a href=\"#usage-selection-controls\" aria-label=\"usage selection controls permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Usage: Selection controls</h2>\n<p>Use selection controls to enable users to select from a predetermined set of options. Choose controls based on the the following considerations:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>How many options do you have to present to the user?</li>\n<li>How many items does the user need to be able to select?</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"checkbox\"><a href=\"#checkbox\" aria-label=\"checkbox permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Checkbox</h3>\n<p>Use checkboxes to allow users to choose <strong>one or more items</strong> from a list of possible choices.</p>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/v4/static/3de304ec4e38a5cb3ce0d5b3f85df927/e692d/checkbox-vertical.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 87px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 55.172413793103445%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"Checkboxes\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/v4/static/3de304ec4e38a5cb3ce0d5b3f85df927/e692d/checkbox-vertical.png\"\n        srcset=\"/v4/static/3de304ec4e38a5cb3ce0d5b3f85df927/e692d/checkbox-vertical.png 87w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 87px) 100vw, 87px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<p>You can also use a single checkbox to allow a user enable or disable a feature or setting.</p>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/v4/static/b4ba215488470f2be07c083bdd703a2a/6b181/one-checkbox.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 125px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 12.8%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"One checkbox\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/v4/static/b4ba215488470f2be07c083bdd703a2a/6b181/one-checkbox.png\"\n        srcset=\"/v4/static/b4ba215488470f2be07c083bdd703a2a/6b181/one-checkbox.png 125w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 125px) 100vw, 125px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<p><strong>When not to use</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Don't use checkboxes for lists that are longer than 5 items. Instead, use a <a href=\"#select-lists\">select list</a>.</li>\n<li>Don't use checkboxes for lists where the user can only select one mutually exclusive option. Instead, use <a href=\"#radio-buttons\">radio buttons</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Labeling and alignment</strong>\nCheckbox labels fall to the right of the checkbox control.</p>\n<p>You can use headings to label a group of checkboxes. Placement of headings will depend on the layout of other content in the form or on the page you’re designing. The checkbox control should always be aligned with the left edge of other controls or input fields in the form or on the page.</p>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/v4/static/e4c66cc9b1792c6377714c2331a2818f/b395b/group-checkbox.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 368px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 62.22826086956522%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"Grouped checkboxes\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/v4/static/e4c66cc9b1792c6377714c2331a2818f/b395b/group-checkbox.png\"\n        srcset=\"/v4/static/e4c66cc9b1792c6377714c2331a2818f/52d5c/group-checkbox.png 175w,\n/v4/static/e4c66cc9b1792c6377714c2331a2818f/1bae2/group-checkbox.png 350w,\n/v4/static/e4c66cc9b1792c6377714c2331a2818f/b395b/group-checkbox.png 368w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 368px) 100vw, 368px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<p>Whenever possible, arrange the checkboxes in a vertical list.</p>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/v4/static/f54e08c59a2854c88ce703dd4c3834b0/064a4/vertical.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 225px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 75.99999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"Vertical checkboxes\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/v4/static/f54e08c59a2854c88ce703dd4c3834b0/064a4/vertical.png\"\n        srcset=\"/v4/static/f54e08c59a2854c88ce703dd4c3834b0/52d5c/vertical.png 175w,\n/v4/static/f54e08c59a2854c88ce703dd4c3834b0/064a4/vertical.png 225w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 225px) 100vw, 225px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<p>If you have space constraints (and your labels are short) you can also use a multi-column grid.</p>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/v4/static/df5693df665e2e3fe8c9a7c8c3eb79a6/b70fd/horizontal.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 471px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 18.89596602972399%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAAECAYAAACOXx+WAAAACXBIWXMAAAsSAAALEgHS3X78AAAAeElEQVQY03WPOxKDMAwFuf/ZOEKGQkqsL2nS+0VAJg12sY1nZ+W3mDtMFWZ2Q+s9IpCZOL2B8/P64RSfRVoDEYP5DhFBKvreE6EC4rFXdBG5gg9qeDFNg2GKTRLrJpAnD4+X11t97AyqOXwy5SBrskWCNeA+9f6Tv0EQJ+1Wj/hxAAAAAElFTkSuQmCC'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"Horizontal checkboxes\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/v4/static/df5693df665e2e3fe8c9a7c8c3eb79a6/b70fd/horizontal.png\"\n        srcset=\"/v4/static/df5693df665e2e3fe8c9a7c8c3eb79a6/52d5c/horizontal.png 175w,\n/v4/static/df5693df665e2e3fe8c9a7c8c3eb79a6/1bae2/horizontal.png 350w,\n/v4/static/df5693df665e2e3fe8c9a7c8c3eb79a6/b70fd/horizontal.png 471w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 471px) 100vw, 471px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<p>You can nest other controls underneath a checkbox. Enable and disable nested options when the user selects or de-selects a checkbox.</p>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/v4/static/648af4609a6b856161e0f13518a20e47/841f8/nested-controls.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 533px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 50.84427767354597%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"Nested checkbox\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/v4/static/648af4609a6b856161e0f13518a20e47/841f8/nested-controls.png\"\n        srcset=\"/v4/static/648af4609a6b856161e0f13518a20e47/52d5c/nested-controls.png 175w,\n/v4/static/648af4609a6b856161e0f13518a20e47/1bae2/nested-controls.png 350w,\n/v4/static/648af4609a6b856161e0f13518a20e47/841f8/nested-controls.png 533w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 533px) 100vw, 533px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<h3 id=\"radio-buttons\"><a href=\"#radio-buttons\" aria-label=\"radio buttons permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Radio buttons</h3>\n<p>Use radio buttons to allow users to select <strong>one item</strong> from a list of possible choices.</p>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/v4/static/81aee6be4c49752a11684a6c55644d36/1a6f1/radio.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 139px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 57.55395683453237%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"Radio buttons\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/v4/static/81aee6be4c49752a11684a6c55644d36/1a6f1/radio.png\"\n        srcset=\"/v4/static/81aee6be4c49752a11684a6c55644d36/1a6f1/radio.png 139w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 139px) 100vw, 139px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Use radio buttons when a user needs to make one mutually exclusive choice. Only one option can be selected at a time.</li>\n<li>A default option should always be selected for the user. If the user selects a different option, the default option is deselected.</li>\n<li>To enable the user to select a null option, provide a radio button with the label “None.”</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>When not to use</strong>\nDo not use a radio button when you have more than 5 options to provide to the user. Instead, use a <a href=\"#select-lists\">select list</a>.  </p>\n<p><strong>Labeling and alignment</strong>\nRadio button labels fall to the right of the radio button control.</p>\n<p>Arrange radio buttons vertically or horizontally depending on space considerations. Vertically arranged radio buttons are easier to scan and are the preferred arrangement.</p>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/v4/static/6c26b8fd32ed8a7f3985123b5d23c6d0/064a4/vertical-radio.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 225px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 69.33333333333334%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"Vertical radio buttons\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/v4/static/6c26b8fd32ed8a7f3985123b5d23c6d0/064a4/vertical-radio.png\"\n        srcset=\"/v4/static/6c26b8fd32ed8a7f3985123b5d23c6d0/52d5c/vertical-radio.png 175w,\n/v4/static/6c26b8fd32ed8a7f3985123b5d23c6d0/064a4/vertical-radio.png 225w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 225px) 100vw, 225px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/v4/static/e3b8fb0025dc24c169ff8079608cd4f4/101aa/horizontal-radio.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 466px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 19.95708154506438%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAAECAYAAACOXx+WAAAACXBIWXMAAAsSAAALEgHS3X78AAAAWklEQVQY042PsQ3AMAgEvf94WSAS4MiAd/gII3dGSXENOh6+uTvMDGMMqOqROSf+es1M0XsHEZVEUCyISOkw8zraLjLc8kA4hyd24D5cefmhR52sVBHi5st7AVb+KHJhMW3QAAAAAElFTkSuQmCC'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"Horizontal radio buttons\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/v4/static/e3b8fb0025dc24c169ff8079608cd4f4/101aa/horizontal-radio.png\"\n        srcset=\"/v4/static/e3b8fb0025dc24c169ff8079608cd4f4/52d5c/horizontal-radio.png 175w,\n/v4/static/e3b8fb0025dc24c169ff8079608cd4f4/1bae2/horizontal-radio.png 350w,\n/v4/static/e3b8fb0025dc24c169ff8079608cd4f4/101aa/horizontal-radio.png 466w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 466px) 100vw, 466px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<p>If necessary, you can use radio buttons to nest other controls.</p>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/v4/static/6cfdc9739dc5e9d7c8c3922248312b7b/fd7a0/nested-radio.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 535px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 50.65420560747664%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"Nested radio buttons\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/v4/static/6cfdc9739dc5e9d7c8c3922248312b7b/fd7a0/nested-radio.png\"\n        srcset=\"/v4/static/6cfdc9739dc5e9d7c8c3922248312b7b/52d5c/nested-radio.png 175w,\n/v4/static/6cfdc9739dc5e9d7c8c3922248312b7b/1bae2/nested-radio.png 350w,\n/v4/static/6cfdc9739dc5e9d7c8c3922248312b7b/fd7a0/nested-radio.png 535w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 535px) 100vw, 535px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<h3 id=\"select-lists\"><a href=\"#select-lists\" aria-label=\"select lists permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Select lists</h3>\n<p>Use a select list to enable users to select one or more items from a list. Select lists should also be used when options are dynamic or variable.</p>\n<p>PatternFly offers several variations of select list:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Single select enables users to select a single, mutually exclusive option.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/v4/static/67d4a1b599f81847f26443e8a7389f67/9973b/selectlist.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 204px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 133.8235294117647%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"Single select\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/v4/static/67d4a1b599f81847f26443e8a7389f67/9973b/selectlist.png\"\n        srcset=\"/v4/static/67d4a1b599f81847f26443e8a7389f67/52d5c/selectlist.png 175w,\n/v4/static/67d4a1b599f81847f26443e8a7389f67/9973b/selectlist.png 204w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 204px) 100vw, 204px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Multi-select enables users to select one or more options.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/v4/static/e5a61ee32109855f9eea2b6f3c41232a/91d6a/selectlist-multi.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 364px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"Multi-select\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/v4/static/e5a61ee32109855f9eea2b6f3c41232a/91d6a/selectlist-multi.png\"\n        srcset=\"/v4/static/e5a61ee32109855f9eea2b6f3c41232a/52d5c/selectlist-multi.png 175w,\n/v4/static/e5a61ee32109855f9eea2b6f3c41232a/1bae2/selectlist-multi.png 350w,\n/v4/static/e5a61ee32109855f9eea2b6f3c41232a/91d6a/selectlist-multi.png 364w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 364px) 100vw, 364px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Typeahead is available for all select lists when you have lists with more than ten options. Typeahead enables users to type into an input field to narrow the list of available options that is displayed.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/v4/static/602a7294a99661f12637881651da6380/1eee6/typeahead.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 246px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 82.52032520325203%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"Typeahead\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/v4/static/602a7294a99661f12637881651da6380/1eee6/typeahead.png\"\n        srcset=\"/v4/static/602a7294a99661f12637881651da6380/52d5c/typeahead.png 175w,\n/v4/static/602a7294a99661f12637881651da6380/1eee6/typeahead.png 246w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 246px) 100vw, 246px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<p>When providing fewer than five options, you can use <a href=\"#radio-buttons\">radio buttons</a> or <a href=\"#checkboxes\">checkboxes</a> to display all options to the user simultaneously if you don’t have any space constraints.</p>\n<h3 id=\"switch\"><a href=\"#switch\" aria-label=\"switch permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Switch</h3>\n<p>Provide a switch to allow users to instantly toggle between an enabled or disabled state.</p>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/v4/static/9f93fdbeef7270fef2a21b591fee6d1c/66a76/switch.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 83px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 83.13253012048193%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"Switch\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/v4/static/9f93fdbeef7270fef2a21b591fee6d1c/66a76/switch.png\"\n        srcset=\"/v4/static/9f93fdbeef7270fef2a21b591fee6d1c/66a76/switch.png 83w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 83px) 100vw, 83px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Label your switch with the affected attribute or capability.</li>\n<li>Don’t use a switch if the options you’re presenting to the user are anything other than “on” or “off.” Instead, use radio buttons.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"usage-bound-entry-controls\"><a href=\"#usage-bound-entry-controls\" aria-label=\"usage bound entry controls permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Usage: Bound-entry controls</h2>\n<p>Use bound-entry controls to enable users to enter special data types, such as dates, times, and other numeric data. Bound-entry controls constrain user input and combine keyboard and mouse interaction. These controls are designed to only allow valid inputs. As a result, field should be is unnecessary.</p>\n<p>Components coming soon!</p>\n<h3 id=\"datepicker\"><a href=\"#datepicker\" aria-label=\"datepicker permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Datepicker</h3>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/v4/static/ff8e31672606b10a34f7d2083fedf5ab/b4523/datepicker.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 525px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 90.28571428571429%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"Datepicker\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/v4/static/ff8e31672606b10a34f7d2083fedf5ab/b4523/datepicker.png\"\n        srcset=\"/v4/static/ff8e31672606b10a34f7d2083fedf5ab/52d5c/datepicker.png 175w,\n/v4/static/ff8e31672606b10a34f7d2083fedf5ab/1bae2/datepicker.png 350w,\n/v4/static/ff8e31672606b10a34f7d2083fedf5ab/b4523/datepicker.png 525w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 525px) 100vw, 525px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<h3 id=\"slider\"><a href=\"#slider\" aria-label=\"slider permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Slider</h3>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/v4/static/42cd119e38c89f4d7dd3d79f77c7c712/f77a2/slider.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 248px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 6.451612903225806%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAABCAYAAADeko4lAAAACXBIWXMAAAsSAAALEgHS3X78AAAAPUlEQVQI12OwXnrbw2LJHS/Lpbc9LZbewY+X3PayWHzL23XDM0eG9AX7TOpXTPr/+ZHNsdPnfC5cuOAJwgByPysUkCQc8wAAAABJRU5ErkJggg=='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"Slider\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/v4/static/42cd119e38c89f4d7dd3d79f77c7c712/f77a2/slider.png\"\n        srcset=\"/v4/static/42cd119e38c89f4d7dd3d79f77c7c712/52d5c/slider.png 175w,\n/v4/static/42cd119e38c89f4d7dd3d79f77c7c712/f77a2/slider.png 248w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 248px) 100vw, 248px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<h2 id=\"errors-and-validation\"><a href=\"#errors-and-validation\" aria-label=\"errors and validation permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Errors and validation</h2>\n<p>In general, data input controls should work to help users avoid input errors. Do your best to disable options that might result in an error, and provide input components that help the user provide accurate data in the correct format. For example, a datepicker is better than a text field when asking users to provide a date because it helps to enforce the appropriate syntax.</p>\n<p>For situations where you do need to provide validation and errors, it is best to provide inline errors as soon as a field leaves focus.</p>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/v4/static/c64cc9b2f3b264fdb2d3518a855f3ec3/8d449/input-error%202.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 160px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 51.87500000000001%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"Error\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/v4/static/c64cc9b2f3b264fdb2d3518a855f3ec3/8d449/input-error%202.png\"\n        srcset=\"/v4/static/c64cc9b2f3b264fdb2d3518a855f3ec3/8d449/input-error%202.png 160w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 160px) 100vw, 160px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<p>For more information about providing validation and errors for data input, see the <a href=\"/v4/design-guidelines/usage-and-behavior/forms#provide-errors-and-validation\">forms design guidelines</a>.</p>","frontmatter":{"path":"/design-guidelines/usage-and-behavior/data-input"}},"allGetStartedNavigationJson":{"edges":[{"node":{"text":"About","path":"/get-started/about"}},{"node":{"text":"Develop","path":"/get-started/developers"}},{"node":{"text":"Design","path":"/get-started/designers"}}]},"allDesignGuidelinesNavigationJson":{"edges":[{"node":{"text":"Styles","path":"/design-guidelines/styles/","subNav":[{"text":"Icons","path":"/design-guidelines/styles/icons"},{"text":"Typography","path":"/design-guidelines/styles/typography"}]}},{"node":{"text":"Usage and behavior","path":"/design-guidelines/usage-and-behavior/","subNav":[{"text":"About modal","path":"/design-guidelines/usage-and-behavior/about-modal"},{"text":"Alerts and notifications","path":"/design-guidelines/usage-and-behavior/alerts-and-notifications"},{"text":"Buttons and links","path":"/design-guidelines/usage-and-behavior/buttons-and-links"},{"text":"Data input","path":"/design-guidelines/usage-and-behavior/data-input"},{"text":"Filters","path":"/design-guidelines/usage-and-behavior/filters"},{"text":"Forms","path":"/design-guidelines/usage-and-behavior/forms"},{"text":"Lists and tables","path":"/design-guidelines/usage-and-behavior/lists-and-tables"},{"text":"Login","path":"/design-guidelines/usage-and-behavior/login"},{"text":"Modal","path":"/design-guidelines/usage-and-behavior/modal"},{"text":"Navigation system","path":"/design-guidelines/usage-and-behavior/navigation-system"},{"text":"Progress bar","path":"/design-guidelines/usage-and-behavior/progress-bar"},{"text":"Toolbar","path":"/design-guidelines/usage-and-behavior/toolbar"}]}},{"node":{"text":"Content","path":"/design-guidelines/content","subNav":[{"text":"Writing","path":"/design-guidelines/content/writing"},{"text":"Voice","path":"/design-guidelines/content/voice-and-tone"},{"text":"Style guide","path":"/design-guidelines/content/grammar-and-terminology"}]}}]}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false}}